  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h3>Travel Insurance - Essential for Complete Peace of Mind on Holiday</h3>
<p><strong>Inghams has partnered with Fogg Travel to offer great travel insurance cover for UK residents.</strong></p>
<p>Whether you're walking, cycling, sightseeing or just kicking back and relaxing, our travel insurance offers policies amongst the best in the market. And for all your ski insurance needs you are in good hands as Fogg insure the British Ski Teams - from Alpine to Freestyle - so not surprisingly, our Winter Sports policies all cover skiing off-piste*.</p>
<h4><strong>Purchasing travel insurance with your holiday booking.</strong></h4>
<p><strong>When booking your holiday, </strong><strong>we strongly recommend you</strong><strong> add travel insurance during the booking process</strong><strong>. </strong><br />You can also be able to view the policy details and the insurance policy.  If you purchase insurance with your holiday booking, you will receive your insurance policy with your booking confirmation.</p>
<h4><strong>Purchasing travel insurance online</strong></h4>
<p>You can arrange cover at any time directly with our partners Fogg.  Booking is simple and secure - just click the link below and choose the policy you require from the selection shown for an instant quote. Please note, Inghams acts only as agent for the Provider in respect of all “Fogg Insurance” services. This link will open in a new window:</p>
