<p><strong>Fogg Travel Insurance Services Limited</strong> with TokioMarine Europe Insurance Ltd and Union Reiseversicherung AG (URV) are authorised and regulated by the <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.fsa.gov.uk/">Financial Conduct Authority</a> (FCA). We are an Appointed Representative of Fogg enabling us to arrange your insurance.We have many years of experience and believe that the cover arranged is well suited to your needs. For our Winter Sports policies you will receive a Fogg Travel ‘Medi-card’ which gives immediate confirmation of cover to doctors and rescue services. Once accepted, all you will have to pay is the policy excess amount. The policy is designed only for permanent residents of the UK and Republic of Ireland.<strong><br /></strong></p>
<p>*Off-piste cover is included provided you act reasonably and do not ski in a closed or avalanche risk area, and if not skiing with a Guide or Instructor, always check that the area is suitable for a skier at your level.</p>
<h3>Cover available for guests 65+</h3>
<p>We offer one of the best travel insurances available, arranged through Fogg Travel Insurance Services Ltd with Tokio Marine Insurance and/ or Reiseversicherung AG (URV) who are authorised and regulated by the Financial Services Authority (FSA). We have many years of experience and that the cover arranged is well suited to your needs.</p>
