<h3>Other General Conditions</h3>
<p>The cover is subject to the conditions and exclusions of the policy and we strongly recommend that you read the full policy wording, which can be viewed at <strong><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="/{localLink:5cb334e1-de5f-4f0e-8e6d-bbea38484c68}" target="_blank" title="Insurance">HERE</a></strong> The policy is designed only for permanent residents of the UK and Republic of Ireland. The age limit for this policy is under 85 years at the date of departure (under 65 for annual multi-trip). If you have any medical condition including anyone on whom the travel plans depend please refer to the <strong>Health</strong> section under <strong>Important Notes</strong> listed below. These details are not a substitute for your insurance policy. <strong>Please read your insurance policy carefully.</strong></p>
<h3>How to Book</h3>
<p>The Fogg travel insurance policy is only available by clicking on the insurance link <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="/{localLink:5cb334e1-de5f-4f0e-8e6d-bbea38484c68}" target="_blank" title="Insurance"><strong>HERE</strong></a> Premiums are payable direct to Fogg and your insurance contract is with them and not Inghams. Your insurance bpolicy will be issued by Fogg.</p>
